From @tvjc @end|ng |rom ch@nn|ng@h@rv@rd@edu  Sat Jul 20 02:58:49 2002
From: @tvjc @end|ng |rom ch@nn|ng@h@rv@rd@edu (Vincent J. Carey, Jr.)
